\par \pard \qc \li1200\ri1200 \sb0 \fi0 BRIEF OF THE NATIONAL ASSOCIATION FOR THE ADVANCEMENT OF COLORED PEOPLE AND THE CITIZENS' COMMISSION ON CIVIL RIGHTS AS AMICI CURIAE IN SUPPORT OF RESPONDENTS
